Package com.n9mtq4.logwindow.listener

This package contains classes having to do with listeners that can be added to the BaseConsole

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdditionListener
    Interface for classes that wish to get notified when the listener is added.
    ConsoleListener
    Interface for classes that wish to get everything.
    DisableListener
    Interface for classes that wish to get notified when the listener is disabled.
    EnableListener
    Interface for classes that wish to get notified when the listener is enabled.
    ListenerAttribute
    Created by will on 8/13/15 at 3:42 PM.
    This interface is extended by AdditionListener, EnableListener, ObjectListener, DisableListener, and RemovalListener.
    ObjectListener
    Interface for classes that wish to get notified when the listener is sent an object.
    RemovalListener
    Interface for classes that wish to get notified when the listener is removed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ListenerContainer
    A class that wraps a ListenerAttribute for use on a BaseConsole.
